# MockMate — developer key config. Copy to `.env` (gitignored) and fill in.
#   cp .env.example .env
# The dev server (server.js :3002), the managed backend (:4000), and Electron all read this
# on launch, so you never re-enter keys through the UI while developing.
#
# MINIMUM TO TEST BOTH FEATURES END-TO-END:  one LLM key  +  DEEPGRAM_API_KEY
# Cheapest path: GEMINI (free) + DEEPGRAM (free $200 credit) covers Solo, Live, and screen-solve.

# ── LLM providers (pick at least one) ────────────────────────────────────────
# Powers: Solo interviewer + evaluation, Live answer hints. Add a 2nd key for auto-failover.

# Google Gemini — FREE tier, also does vision (screen "Solve it").  https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# OpenAI — GPT-5.4 (quality) / GPT-4o / mini (fast) + vision. Pay-per-use.  https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=
# OPENAI_GPT5_MODEL=gpt-5.4     # override the GPT-5.4 entry's id (e.g. gpt-5.5)
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o           # override the GPT-4o entry's id
# OPENAI_MINI_MODEL=gpt-5-mini  # modernize the fast-tier mini (default gpt-4o-mini)

# Groq — FREE, very fast (Llama 3.3 70B, LPU). Low free limits.       https://console.groq.com/keys
GROQ_API_KEY=

# Cerebras — FREE, fastest throughput (wafer-scale). OpenAI-compatible.  https://cloud.cerebras.ai
CEREBRAS_API_KEY=
# CEREBRAS_MODEL=llama-3.3-70b

# Anthropic Claude — Opus 4.8 / Sonnet 5 / Haiku 4.5. Pay-per-use.   https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Google Gemini overrides (ids drift — override if the default 404s):
# GEMINI_FLASH_LITE_MODEL=gemini-3.1-flash-lite   # fast-tier default (lowest TTFT)
# GEMINI_3_MODEL=gemini-3-flash
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash

# Any OpenAI-compatible endpoint (self-hosted / other providers).
# LLM_API_KEY=
# LLM_BASE_URL=
# LLM_MODEL=

# ── Live Interview: speech-to-text (REQUIRED for Live) ───────────────────────
# Transcribes the interviewer's voice in real time (Deepgram nova-2).  https://console.deepgram.com
DEEPGRAM_API_KEY=

# ── Optional: web-search grounding for company/current-events questions ──────
# TAVILY_API_KEY=            # https://tavily.com
# SERPER_API_KEY=            # https://serper.dev

# ── Optional: LOCAL on-site jobs in Job Matching (Adzuna, free) ──────────────
# Without these, Jobs shows REMOTE roles only (region-filtered). Add them to also get
# city-level on-site jobs for your location (e.g. Hyderabad). https://developer.adzuna.com
# ADZUNA_APP_ID=
# ADZUNA_APP_KEY=

# ── Optional: Duo / Rooms (live collaborative interview help via LiveKit) ────
# A friend/mentor joins your interview room live — shared transcript + screen + private AI co-pilot.
# Free tier at LiveKit Cloud: https://cloud.livekit.io  (or self-host livekit-server).
# LIVEKIT_URL=wss://<your-project>.livekit.cloud
# LIVEKIT_API_KEY=
# LIVEKIT_API_SECRET=
